&lt;p&gt;Reporting into our General Counsel, you will partner closely with Product, Engineering, Clinical, Data Science, Sale, Client Support and Compliance teams to navigate complex regulatory requirements, shape product features, support commercial transactions and support responsible AI development. You will also help address emerging legal needs as Hello Heart continues to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
